206. Reverse Linked List

Solution - 
Time Complexity - O(n)
Space Complexity - O(1)

```
# Definition for singly-linked list.
# class ListNode:
#     def __init__(self, val=0, next=None):
#         self.val = val
#         self.next = next
class Solution:
    def reverseList(self, head: Optional[ListNode]) -> Optional[ListNode]:
        prev = None #for pointing nodes backward
        curr = head #for current pointer
        while head:
            curr = head.next
            head.next = prev
            prev = head
            head = curr
        
        return prev
```
